    <title>CTF中的htaccess</title>
    <url>/2020/05/07/CTF%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84htaccess/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>服务器中间件为apache，因此想到了传.htaceess来解析php，通常我们用</p>
<p>.htaccess来解析非php后缀文件时用到</p>
<p><code>AddType application/x-httpd-php .ppp</code></p>
<p>或者</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;FilesMatch &quot;shell.jpg&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"> SetHandler application/x-httpd-php</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/FilesMatch&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><code>auto_append_file</code>和<code>auto_prepend_file</code></p>
<h2 id="相关bypass"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#相关bypass"></a> 相关bypass</h2>
<p>如果文件末尾被自动加上一句话,会导致服务器500错误,这时候可以在最后添加<code>#\</code>将换行转义成普通字符</p>
<p>如果特殊字符被实体编码, 可以通过特殊编码来绕过</p>
<p><img alt="run php without &lt;" data-src="https://res.cloudinary.com/durtftgrv/image/upload/v1567047922/blog/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7_2019-08-29_%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.05.09_hvkhnw.png" class="lozad"></p>
<p><img alt="image-20200507104758918" data-src="/2020/05/07/CTF中的htaccess/image-20200507104758918.png" class="lozad"></p>
