<p>添加<code>&lt;pref name=&quot;ByteBuffer.TempDir&quot;&gt;/tmp&lt;/pref&gt;</code></p>
<p><img alt="image-20200317233142178" data-src="/2020/03/17/Bless-Hex-Editor保存错误/image-20200317233142178.png" class="lozad"></p>
]]></content>
