<p>本来想用system()直接读的,disable_funcionts禁了</p>
<p><a href="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023164845633-609154986.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="img" data-src="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023164845633-609154986.png" class="lozad"></a></p>
