<p><a href="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023165126001-611951825.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="img" data-src="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023165126001-611951825.png" class="lozad"></a></p>
<p>还有种方法就是还是用数学函数来实现,payload:</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`base_convert``(2146934604002,10,36)(hex2bin(``dechex``(47)).``base_convert``(25254448,10,36))`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>http走私是由于前端代理服务器和后端源服务器之间的一些差异导致请求走私。</p>
<p>通过CL-CL的方法来执行</p>
<p><a href="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023232536793-1722711057.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="img" data-src="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023232536793-1722711057.png" class="lozad"></a></p>
<p><a href="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023234413665-446290653.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="img" data-src="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023234413665-446290653.png" class="lozad"></a></p>
<p>利用CL-TE或者TE-CL</p>
<p>根据我的理解，其实对于这道题都一样，前端代理和后端源都会执行一遍get传参，前端代理有waf，后端源执行返回正常的。</p>
<p><a href="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023234858358-1760182999.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="img" data-src="https://img2018.cnblogs.com/blog/1357258/201910/1357258-20191023234858358-1760182999.png" class="lozad"></a></p>
