    <title>Firstpaper</title>
    <url>/2019/10/13/Firstpaper/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="katex"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#katex"></a> KaTex</h1>
<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mspace width="2em"></mspace><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace width="1em"></mspace><msubsup><mi>b</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>j</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></msubsup><mspace width="1em"></mspace><msup><mi>e</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">≠</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mi>e</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mspace width="1em"></mspace><msup><mi>e</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msup></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(1)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">a_{1}\qquad x^2 \quad  b^{3}_{ij} \quad e^{2}\neq (e^x)^2 \quad e^{x^2}\tag{1} 
