    <title>Firstpaper</title>
    <url>/2019/10/13/can-not-get-apt-lock/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="问题e-could-not-get-lock-varlibdpkglock-open-11-resource-temporarily-unavailable"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#问题e-could-not-get-lock-varlibdpkglock-open-11-resource-temporarily-unavailable"></a> 问题：E: Could not get lock /var/lib/dpkg/lock – open (11: Resource temporarily unavailable)</h1>
<p>E: Could not get lock /var/lib/dpkg/lock - open (11: Resource temporarily unavailable)<br>
E: Unable to lock the administration directory (/var/lib/dpkg/), is another process using it?</p>
<p><img alt="image-20191115085638473" data-src="/2019/10/13/can-not-get-apt-lock/image-20191115085638473.png" class="lozad"></p>
<h1 id="解决"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#解决"></a> 解决</h1>
<p>因为有另外一个程序在运行，导致锁不可用。原因可能是上次运行更新或安装没有正常完成。解决办法是杀死此进程</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo rm /var/cache/apt/archives/lock</span><br><span class="line">sudo rm /var/lib/dpkg/lock</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --configure -a</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
